{"tid":845912,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《紐時》揭中國山寨廠續排放被禁化合物　損臭氧層　問題或是冰山一角","createTime":"2018-10-03T04:48:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-03T06:19:15.000Z","uid":47714,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"927a39974c12be7e7226a10297443d0c530f39e1","tid":845912,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T04:48:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/nature/紐時-揭中國山寨廠續排放被禁化合物-損臭氧層-問題或是冰山一角/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fnature%2F%E7%B4%90%E6%99%82-%E6%8F%AD%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%B1%B1%E5%AF%A8%E5%BB%A0%E7%BA%8C%E6%8E%92%E6%94%BE%E8%A2%AB%E7%A6%81%E5%8C%96%E5%90%88%E7%89%A9-%E6%90%8D%E8%87%AD%E6%B0%A7%E5%B1%A4-%E5%95%8F%E9%A1%8C%E6%88%96%E6%98%AF%E5%86%B0%E5%B1%B1%E4%B8%80%E8%A7%92%2F&d=Aow8GF3K3lDdrXZekHQXT%2FiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=58c8e290\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fnature%2F%E7%B4%90%E6%99%82-%E6%8F%AD%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%B1%B1%E5%AF%A8%E5%BB%A0%E7%BA%8C%E6%8E%92%E6%94%BE%E8%A2%AB%E7%A6%81%E5%8C%96%E5%90%88%E7%89%A9-%E6%90%8D%E8%87%AD%E6%B0%A7%E5%B1%A4-%E5%95%8F%E9%A1%8C%E6%88%96%E6%98%AF%E5%86%B0%E5%B1%B1%E4%B8%80%E8%A7%92%2F&h=98bacbe3\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/nature/紐時-揭中國山寨廠續排放被禁化合物-損臭氧層-問題或是冰山一角/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/pexels-photo-929385_jnZrz_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fpexels-photo-929385_jnZrz_1200x0.png&h=1331b3ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上月《立場新聞》曾報道，其中一種被禁的化合物一氟三氯甲烷 (CFC-11) 排放量竟自 2013 年不斷上升，每年有 1.3 萬公噸被排放至大氣之中。<br />\n<br />\n而《紐約時報》與獨立調查員搜集資料與到中國進行調查，揭發中國內地仍有工廠無視 1987 年簽訂的《蒙特利爾議定書 (Montreal Protocol on Substances that Deplete the Ozone Layer) 》規定逐步淘汰 CFC (Chlorofluorocarbons, 氟氯烴 ) 等多種破壞地球臭氧的化合物，而這些工廠主要以 CFC-11 製作雪櫃與建築物的泡沫隔熱層。<br />\n<br />\n聯合國環境署署長 Erik Solheim 指，已了解《紐時》與 EIA 的調查，並表示製造 CFC-11 是環境罪行，必須有果斷行動阻止中國的排放。他在聲明又指出，現時亦要更深入研究中國 CFC-11 製造問題，現時見到的可能只是冰山一角。"},{"pid":"04c5745ffb38043b479315f1bb1c602bf10cfb71","tid":845912,"uid":11977,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T04:52:57.000Z","msg":"全球反支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19f4140ab51b498e563a5f9191817ae4fcc47311","tid":845912,"uid":200328,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T06:19:15.000Z","msg":"支那係世界最大毒瘤<br />\n應該全世界合作消滅支那"}]}